step_data.thought: The user is already on the 'My Orders' page where their recent orders are displayed. I can see the order details such as order numbers, dates, totals, and statuses. The user can view specific orders by clicking the 'View Order' links available next to each order. I will click on the 'View Order' link for the most recent order to provide detailed information about it.
